p :::s3:::She has to continue pretending that she 's in love with Peeta , or they 'll hurt Gale , Katniss 's oldest friend .
:::s5:::Peeta and Katniss , meanwhile , have had a tense relationship since Peeta found out that Katniss was only pretending to be in love with him during the Games .
p :::s17:::Katniss goes to meet Gale in the woods and tells him everything that 's happened .
:::s20:::Katniss goes to tell Peeta , who agrees to run away , but then , in the town 's main square , they find Gale being publicly whipped for hunting .
p :::s21:::As Gale recuperates , Katniss realizes she loves him and decides not to run away .
